patches.description:
ExtUtils-MakeMaker ~ ExtUtils-MakeMaker-7.38-01-ldopts
Carried forward from 7.30
Make 'perl -MExtUtils::Embed -e ldopts' output a direct reference to libperl.a if using -lperl would pick up libperl.so.
http://bugs.activestate.com/show_bug.cgi?id=39069
p4-change: 152627

ExtUtils-MakeMaker ~ ExtUtils-MakeMaker-7.38-02-html-pods
Carried forward from 7.30
Support for HTML PODs

ExtUtils-MakeMaker ~ ExtUtils-MakeMaker-7.38-03-htmldir
Carried forward from 7.30
Make sure MakeMaker sets up INSTALL.*HTMLDIR when using INSTALL_BASE
Without this change the html docs will be written to root level directories /bin, /lib, and /site (if they are writable; otherwise install will fail).
The INSTALL_BASE feature is used by local::lib (and cpanminus).

ExtUtils-MakeMaker ~ ExtUtils-MakeMaker-7.38-skip-xs-on-AIX
Carried forward from 7.30
Skip EUMM XS tests on AIX.
https://github.com/Perl-Toolchain-Gang/ExtUtils-MakeMaker/pull/278
